ce in HST mock\nobservations, (ii) follow galaxies selected at z=2 to their z=0 descendants,\nand quantify their growth and merger histories, and (iii) track massive z=0\ngalaxies to high redshift and study their joint evolution in star-formation\nactivity and compactness. We conclude with a discussion of several\ndisagreements with observations, and lay out possible directions for future\nresearch.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 15 May 2014 05:54:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 12 Aug 2014 20:27:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-09-26"}
